# Map interactions

- Long press → create memory pin at location
- Tap cluster → zoom in + expand
- Single pin tap → bottom sheet preview; swipe up → full story
- Camera: `flyTo` with **800ms** duration
- `expo-haptics` on map interactions (mobile)

## Performance

- Cluster pins when zoom < 12
- Cache map tiles offline for last 5 viewed areas
